headline: News Corp to Participate in Goldman Sachs Communacopia + Technology Conference
summary: NEW YORK, September 02, 2025--News Corp announced today that Chief Executive Robert Thomson will participate in the Goldman Sachs Communacopia + Technology Conference on Monday, September 8, 2025. The session will begin at 1:10 PM EDT (10:10 AM PDT).
